query:
UPDATE artworks 
SET image_url = JSON_UNQUOTE(JSON_EXTRACT(gallery_images, '$[0]'))
WHERE image_url LIKE '%d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net%' 
AND gallery_images IS NOT NULL 
AND JSON_LENGTH(gallery_images) > 0;
